review.reviewBody: This was one of the best Green Curry Chicken I have had in the Kitsilano area. VERY authentic ingredients and flavour. Absolutely refreshing. So good!!! I wish I had known of this restaurant years ago! Highly recommend!
chicken was terribly dry and curry had no flavor at all! pad thai was meh. this place is way overrated. so expensive.
Delivered hot but flavours lacking a little of the typical Thai spice and herb profiles.
WOW WOW WOW. I can't get enough of the curry dipping sauce that came with the roti, and the pad si ew with crispy pork was just SO delicious!
WOW, WOW, WOW, so delicious! Get the pad si ew with the crispy pork!!!
